                  </persName>
             sworn. - I live in Leicester-square, but know nothing of the robery; I lost one tablespoon and one tea-spoon. 
               <persName id="t18030112-106-person777">
                  MARY 
                  DYMOND
               <interp inst="t18030112-106-person777" type="surname" value="DYMOND"></interp>
